@NODE History "History"

Version 1.0   - Initial release.

Version 1.1   - Fixed a bug which caused numerous enforcer hits, and may have
                crashed some machines.
              - Added the ability to @{"skip certain files" link skip}.
              - Optionally informs the sysop of EVERY upload!

Version 1.2   - Now informs the sysop even if the file type is not
                recognised.
              - Fixed a bug which told the sysop a user had uploaded a
                private file AND they had uploaded a file to area -1.

@ENDNODE
